longBusinessSummary: FluroTech Ltd., a technology and marketing company, focuses on the commercialization of various technologies in the pandemic defense sector. It provides a pandemic defense platform, a saliva-based antigen test that targets active infections evidenced by the presence of live viral particles. The company is headquartered in Calgary, Canada.
